Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己做的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天我要驾驶着自己做的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由翱翔在天空里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的飞机就是指那个自行车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是自行车呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.59,0:02:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叫圣路易斯号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.99,0:02:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你呀 要是大家都像你一样骑着自行车在天上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.73,0:03:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天上就都满满的都是自行车了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的圣路易斯可以飞起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从设计到制作都是我自己一个人一手包办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.76,0:03:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能飞不起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.23,0:03:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是刚才很完美地掉下来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣路易斯号
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九助你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不懂男人的梦想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不用打我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.17,0:03:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  很帅呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很帅?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够热衷于某件事是很帅的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.28,0:03:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广木君 加油呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我自己的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想用圣路易斯号来实现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管他啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙怎么回事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他大概也很迷惘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷惘?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己也不明白到底怎样才能让飞机飞起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 才会那样生气 一个人烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.34,0:04:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也一定需要一起相同梦想的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要是也能成为伙伴就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.93,0:04:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再去帮他加油好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很想看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广木君驾驶飞机的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是梦之世界的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.41,0:04:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法自由自在地飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想的世界是在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.11,0:04:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是… 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.53,0:04:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给天马也看看广木驾驶飞机的样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啊 竟然不敲门就进入淑女的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才是在跟小卫进行秘密的爱之电话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.49,0:05:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没做那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去小卫家里他也是一直在打电话！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后又从你这房间里传出了男人的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫真过分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然和小小兔…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔 你给我从实招来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫的话 今天不是电脑通信的日子么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.46,0:05:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你白天不是这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我要睡了 快出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…抱歉… 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:05:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马的事是我们两个的秘密 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.57,0:06:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉鲁科尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.92,0:06:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没有找到天马吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些小女孩们太不中用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水手战士那群混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再犯同样的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是下一个目标吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个身材匀称的男孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愿意的话就不用勉强去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没说不去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很不情愿的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉帕拉也想去呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:06:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉帕拉也想？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们三个猜拳决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾 这个是我吉恩吉恩的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么时候决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.27,0:07:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候画的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们慢慢泡澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这一手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个就是广木的飞机哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马你看得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害 竟然全部是一个人做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 昨天明明坏的那么严重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经全修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广木真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人嘟囔什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼 可别小看你兔姐的情报网哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也想看看圣路易斯号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:07:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个就是人力飞机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.46,0:07:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是自行车罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是飞机！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.15,0:08:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙耳朵真灵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人力飞机 真了不起的梦想啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎现在要起飞了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广木 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广木 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广木
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广木君 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么飞不起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 亚美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 没事的 就交给亚美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.77,0:09:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人居然能做到这地步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就是要提高空气动力特性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增强机翼的摆动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 你的体力还是不太够
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 的确是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广木君也许有些太瘦弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆做成两人座的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞成 就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的话太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小丽你欺负人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我骑上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.11,0:09:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔你也很了不起呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我一个人的梦想 别管了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 老说这种话是永远不会成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这么小气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翱翔蓝天是人类共同的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱特兄弟也是二人同心协力才取得成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.35,0:10:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你放心 尽量依靠我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 九助
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.05,0:10:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 不用客气 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是男人之间的友情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友情？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后这里 要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 什么都能互相商量的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无话不谈的好朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马 我们两个是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讨厌我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢天马哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.72,0:10:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得无论何时何事都能向你倾诉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是天马你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对天马的事一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都不告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.39,0:10:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 现在还无法跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:11:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以这个姿态出现在你面前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.57,0:11:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就是不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是朋友的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不应该是无话不谈的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.84,0:11:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你其实是没有把我当朋友的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.55,0:11:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不信任我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就无法继续待在你身边了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 请相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回来 天马
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.21,0:12:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你都不回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.50,0:12:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么就这么消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们果然不是真正的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为能够互相理解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了 这么晚还在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.37,0:12:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 我送你回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.53,0:12:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫有和小兔吵过架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是心中所想 什么都能说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧 现在也没什么不能说的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且兔子又是那种藏不住心事的性子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫和小兔是朋友以上的关系呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚了 一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.47,0:12:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管我 反正小兔是没办法理解我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你每次不是偷窥人家的房间就是打听隐私
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是觉得你的样子有些奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想你是不是有什么烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.76,0:13:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那叫多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有很多不能说的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.83,0:13:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不能和你说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马也有不能说的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回去了 在家里等你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 今天一定要成功
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 小小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我在九助的帮助下改造了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.21,0:13:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也采纳了亚美她们的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.26,0:13:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有朋友是好事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.81,0:14:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起一个人做 要好得多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使不用说很多 也可以互相信赖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.23,0:14:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 请相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.97,0:14:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 天马
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.28,0:14:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.54,0:14:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要飞起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去人类曾经无比向往的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.45,0:14:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了在空中飞居然做出了那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是只要想飞不管去哪都轻轻松松
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.88,0:14:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是热爱天空的好伙伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不是什么可疑的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光看你这身打扮就够可疑的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:14:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.91,0:15:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这打扮很可疑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很像普通的女孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要成为你们的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不应该是这种感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 我还以为伪装的很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这群敏锐的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踩在球上飘在空中 不管怎么想都很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然暴露了就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就让我看看你的梦之镜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.15,0:15:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广木君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广木君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀又没中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿那套衣服真是浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉鲁科尼亚老太婆也真是的 老让我们做白工
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不知道该怎么办了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还要靠我来收拾残局
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.21,0:16:16.02,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&FF77FF&}给我住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:20.15,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&FF77FF&}你居然要夺去在天空里 翱翔的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:23.09,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&FF77FF&}广木的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:24.15,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&FF77FF&}绝不原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.14,0:16:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是一个人来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:29.13,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&FF77FF&}爱与正义的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:30.85,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&FF77FF&}水手服美少女战士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:32.37,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&FF77FF&}水手小月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在问你你今天是一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:38.94,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&FF77FF&}要代替月亮 惩罚你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.59,0:16:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问你今天是一个人来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对付你这种人 我一个人就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然敢这么对我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来吧 我的放射线妖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食梦长毛象  帕欧帕欧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.93,0:17:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕欧帕欧 我是食梦长毛象 帕欧帕欧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕欧帕欧的力量也很强大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.37,0:17:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕欧帕欧 顺便把那个梦之镜也吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.96,0:17:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.43,0:17:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就乖乖待在那里交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.06,0:17:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕欧帕欧 给我干掉他们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:49.57,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2626FF&}火星 烈焰狙击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:56.30,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFDC228&}水星 水之狂想曲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在 水手小月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:07.64,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&FF77FF&}拜托了 天马
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.00,0:18:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.89,0:18:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马已经不会再来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经没有再呼唤天马的资格了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道怎么回事但是个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.31,0:18:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水手月亮 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 这点小伤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不知道你们之间发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你应该更相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.08,0:18:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:19:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都很喜欢小月亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.09,0:19:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请相信我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 水手月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕欧帕欧 你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:23.32,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&FF77FF&}拜托了 天马
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:25.74,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&FF77FF&}请你守护大家的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:32.33,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&FF77FF&}闪烁呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.60,0:19:59.22,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}月亮华丽冥想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退出舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马 你来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为你相信梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 天马
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 要飞了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.23,0:20:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九助 要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一定要飞起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.74,0:21:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信的力量好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.57,0:21:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你依然相信梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无论何时都会在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.34,0:21:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也要相信天马
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 相信的力量居然可以产生这么美妙的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.96,0:22:02.18,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啦啦啦  绝不放弃  继续努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:06.18,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这场胜负全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.43,0:22:10.27,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期盼的热情加速了我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.27,0:22:17.23,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在青春期的年纪 恋爱的轮廓总是不停的转变
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.91,0:22:32.54,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后  我对一位偷心者一见钟情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.04,0:22:40.38,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他如同过往的情人  乱了我的情绪  不知是否会再度受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.80,0:22:47.43,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办？ 但我已经决定 想要故意捉弄他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.85,0:22:57.02,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飘扬于风中的水手服  我要坦荡荡地做自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.44,0:23:02.86,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啦啦啦 绝不放弃  继续努力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.86,0:23:07.12,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次就轮到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:10.83,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧张的悸动加速了我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.83,0:23:17.96,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在青春期的年纪 恋爱的轮廓总是不停的转变
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.85,0:23:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被互换身体了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.59,0:23:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修长的手脚 丰满的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.34,0:23:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不是小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.73,0:23:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别以为这样就实现梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.60,0:23:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是想变回轻松学习的小学生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.91,0:23:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级水手月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.42,0:23:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马的秘密 守护梦想世界的美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.87,0:23:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月光传递着爱的讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
